overview: A disgruntled employee finds out he has to work late. Lucky for him, his boss just won't leave him alone.  After working long hours a worker decides to take a at the office and awakes to a well deserved surprise.  The boss isn't too pleased to find one of his employees watching porn during work hours.  A worker is having a hard time making a sales call when his colleague keeps distracting him.  When an employee mouths off to his supervisor he finds himself in deep, deep, trouble.
title: Office Twinks 2
